without one.

19:50.731 --> 19:53.067
You got a cell phone?

19:53.150 --> 19:54.568
Yeah.

19:56.779 --> 19:58.823
I'm gonna take that
for now.

19:58.906 --> 20:00.032
What else?

20:00.116 --> 20:03.202
