you're not carrying
any weapons or explosives.

20:27.143 --> 20:28.561
( clears throat )

20:35.693 --> 20:37.319
Wow.

20:37.403 --> 20:40.281
So, Dr. Hill,
what's your spiel?

20:40.364 --> 20:42.825
‐ Call me Eugene.
‐ OK, Eugene.

20:44.243 --> 20:47.621
‐ <i>Dr.</i> Eugene.
‐ Dr. Merian.

20:47.705 --> 20:49.248
( laughs )

20:51.125 --> 20:53.878
