<i>Hey, it's Andy.</i>
<i>Please leave a message.</i>

24:00.439 --> 24:02.608
‐ <i>( beep )</i>
‐ Hey.

24:04.151 --> 24:06.278
It's me. Um...

24:08.155 --> 24:11.241
I'm sorry I haven't
called until now. I, uh...

24:11.325 --> 24:13.202
<i>You know how I get.</i>

24:13.285 --> 24:16.705
<i>But I think you</i>
<i>would understand</i>
<i>if you saw this place.</i>

24:16.789 --> 24:20.709
I‐I just finally found
something special.

24:20.793 --> 24:23.087
It's like I've been looking
for it my whole life,

24:23.170 --> 24:25.422
and I don't know what to do.

24:25.506 --> 24:27.925
( voice breaking )
I'm sorry.

24:28.008 --> 24:30.260
Fuck, I'm sorry.

24:30.344 --> 24:31.929
( sighs )

24:32.012 --> 24:33.681
I miss you.

24:35.516 --> 24:38.268
And, um...

24:38.352 --> 24:41.605
I don't know when
I'm gonna be home,

24:41.689 --> 24:45.442
